                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-193-off1000 t18310908-193-cd1001"></join>, 8 pennyweights of silver solder, value 2s.; 2 pennyweights of gold solder, value 18d., and 1 pennyweight of gold and silver solder, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18310908-193-victim1477" type="victimName">
                  John 
